# Testing

- **Tier 1:** `flutter test` (headless widget/unit). Run via `./script/test.sh` or `flutter test`. Keep green after any logic or test change.
- **Tier 2:** Integration tests on device/simulator. Run via `./script/test_integration.sh` or `flutter test integration_test/ -d <device_id>`. Default device ID is in TEST_PLAN.md; pass as argument to override.
- **New runnable behavior:** If the behavior runs on device (e.g. async, native, persistence), add Tier 2 tests and run them before considering the feature done. See TEST_TDD.md and tester skill.
